## Project Structure

```
MapsDataService/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ src/
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ main.rs      # Entry point ‚Äî starts HTTP server + MQTT subscriber
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ config.rs    # Config loaded from environment variables
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ db.rs        # PostgreSQL queries (Haversine nearby + get by ID)
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ models.rs    # Serde + sqlx row types
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ error.rs     # AppError ‚Üí axum HTTP response mapping
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ http.rs      # Axum router and handlers
‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ mqtt.rs      # rumqttc subscriber loop
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Cargo.toml
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Dockerfile
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ .env.example
```

---

## Dependencies

| Crate              | Purpose                        |
|--------------------|--------------------------------|
| `axum`             | HTTP framework                 |
| `sqlx`             | Async PostgreSQL driver        |
| `rumqttc`          | MQTT 5 client                  |
| `tokio`            | Async runtime                  |
| `serde` / `serde_json` | JSON serialisation         |
| `tracing`          | Structured logging             |
| `dotenvy`          | `.env` file loading            |
| `tower-http`       | CORS / trace middleware        |
| `thiserror` / `anyhow` | Error handling             |
